    public final class CloudSimEvent

      • getSerial

        public long getSerial()
        Description copied from interface: SimEvent
        An attribute to help CloudSim to identify the order of received events when multiple events are generated at the same time. If two events have the same SimEvent.getTag(), to know what event is greater than other (i.e. that happens after other), the SimEvent.compareTo(SimEvent) makes use of this field.
        Specified by:
